'''''Happer's Way''''' was a [[Rendili StarDrive/Legends|Rendili StarDrive]] [[heavy freighter]] flown by [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Norello]] out of [[Chandrila/Legends|Chandrila]]. It was contracted by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Imperial Army/Legends|Army]] to bring fifty [[All Terrain Scout Transport/Legends|AT-ST]] walkers to the garrison on [[Llorkan]], but was interrupted in its delivery by an attack from the pirate ship ''[[Cavalcade]]''. The ship and its captain were rescued by [[Emperor's Hand/Legends|Emperor's Hand]] [[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]].

